snippet.textDisplay: I am truly amazed by the comments section. There is so much bad mouthing in other social media platforms against each other (India and Pakistan) . But Coke Studio has done a wonderful job in making us realise that our culture is basically the same and we appreciate each other's music. There are political differences between the two neighbor's, no doubt, but my request is not to dismiss each other at person to person level. Love to Pakistan from India.
